1. *Svakim* danom postajem sve jači. (With every day, I become stronger.)
2. Treba da posetim *svakog* prijatelja u gradu. (I need to visit every friend in the city.)
3. *Svakim* novim izazovom, postajemo bolji. (With every new challenge, we become better.)
4. *Svakog* jutra u sedam sati ustajem. (I wake up every morning at seven o'clock.)
5. *Svakim* korakom približavamo se cilju. (With every step, we get closer to the goal.)
6. Nastavnik je objasnio gradivo *svakom* učeniku posebno. (The teacher explained the material to each student individually.)
7. *Svakom* treba malo vremena da se prilagodi novoj situaciji. (Everyone needs a little time to adjust to a new situation.)
8. Ovo je *svakom* jasno. (This is clear to everyone.)
9. Nema dovoljno hrane za *svakoga*. (There isn't enough food for everyone.)
10. *Svakim* danom sve više uživam u ovoj knjizi. (Every day, I enjoy this book more and more.)